m/a/YQOhrvX</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Hauntologist2]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>One upside to having ADHD is that you gain a new hobby/obsession every week! Here are some of mine:</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/XkZTx6m</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/c1kTG4X.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Post apocalyptic cosplay will always have a dirty place in my heart</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gRPErK4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I love to draw and I was blown away when an Imgurian recently reached out to buy a tattoo commission from me! My art is going to be on someone's body forever!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wd7rPB8.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My last secret Santa where I made a viking style set of coasters and drinking horn holster. Leather work is probably my most rewarding passion.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fGrqZVX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I try my best at baking but it is definitely a science. Here's a Portal cake replica I made for a birthday party.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Uc6WArZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Probably my SO's favorite of my hobbies. Understandable since they get to eat the rejects AND the winners.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tl3nCZH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Bartender by trade. Edible art is great when you can see the transition of happiness in people when they get to taste your concoctions.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VRs8jdt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I love to grow plants and mushrooms alike! I had to fill my home with greenery since I live in the desert.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/sC69Rnh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Needle felting for when I feel like making cute tiny things. I made a replica of my axolotl</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kvyB0hy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Camping is an essential break from the dread I start to feel when work and too many horrible news stories start to pile up. 5/7 would recommend.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tAr8yv4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This is Valley Of Fire State Park, NV. One of my top 3 favorite places to go.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UB0cQR4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Hammy the axolotl tax!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/XkZTx6m</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LANAAAAAAAAAA]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Magic</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/k1vioHA</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FXZjQYw.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/k1vioHA</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[dickSoLong]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>It's nice to be boring, if it means I could function like a regular human being.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/7nJrSOx</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6VD2Ybs.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/7nJrSOx</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Srajo101]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Capybara chew￼</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/qOk3wcE</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/mUBZ0WB.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Capybara stew ^_^ #cute #capybara #cute_animal #wholesome #mildly_interesting</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/qOk3wcE</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[charizardkitty]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The good old days.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/FL8ae7f</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cbkPJA6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/FL8ae7f</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[BeetBoxer]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Nazi/Groypers are here to stay?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/IBYbxNt</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/y7G7WHl.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Watch out for these groypers. Vote locally.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ylziiX5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The dystopia is almost cemented.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yO6QxFn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I don't post this crap to cause anxiety or get points. Awareness is everything. And yes, my anxiety levels are through the roof.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BbZ86DF.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It's time to start preppin' like a lunatic. They are armed. We need to defend ourselves; our human rights and our bodies, our friends and families, our education a'd equality. They are mobilizing a war. Not gearing up, but moving.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4N2JbzU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Remember Sheriff Joe Arapio? https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joe_Arpaio?wprov=sfla1

He believed that Obama wasn't actually American and that his birth certificate was forged? He was a massive racist and misogynist and ruined hundreds of lives.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/E7t0huG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And he is the "good guy" in this group?? Wtf.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1MEhsqC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://www.azmirror.com/2022/02/26/wendy-rogers-racist-white-nationalists-patriots-and-called-for-hanging-political-enemies/</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vteaeWD.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Tax. Prepare yourselves.

FP. Send guns, toilet paper, and animal videos.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/IBYbxNt</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Eucrow]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>English major. Andrew Rudick</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/h6RP3RO</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fmBy5SK.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/h6RP3RO</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[KingMammajamma]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Freedom from religion</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/PFpOjSp</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/znr8xvX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/PFpOjSp</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Maitrify]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>One year on</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/QAGtrwm</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MP6YtzX.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/QAGtrwm</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[vidadobl6]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Internet Gifts - Pt. 523</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/mHDLPHJ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/WBEsONn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>1.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PVhMq4N.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>2.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bcJ2Iso.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>3.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/WwhU0ix.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>4.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/E3jCdeq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>5